shared fakt_kandideeri = let
  // Source data
  Source = koondKeyevents,

  // Group by "date" and "kava" and sum "keyEvents"
  sumKeyevents = Table.Group(Source, {"date", "kava"}, {{"sumkeyevents", each List.Sum([keyEvents]), Int64.Type}}),
  
  // Sort and group by date
  groupbyDate = Table.Sort(
    Table.Group(
      sumKeyevents, {"date"}, 
      {
        {"tbl", each _, type nullable table[date = nullable date, kava = nullable text, sumkeyevents = Int64.Type]},
        {"fullkava", each lookupKava, type table}
      }
    ),
    {"date", Order.Descending}
  ),
  
  // Add the full list of kava to each date
  addFullkavalist = Table.SelectColumns(
    Table.AddColumn(groupbyDate, "Custom", each let 
      list1 = List.Buffer([tbl][sumkeyevents]),
      list0 = List.Buffer([tbl][kava]),
      result = Table.AddColumn([fullkava], "kandideerid", each try list1 {List.PositionOf(list0, [kava])} otherwise null, Int64.Type) 
    in 
      result
    ), 
    {"date", "Custom"}
  ),

  // Expand to individual rows
  #"Expanded Custom" = Table.ExpandTableColumn(addFullkavalist, "Custom", {"kava", "kandideerid"}, {"kava", "kandideerid"}),
  #"Changed column type" = Table.TransformColumnTypes(#"Expanded Custom", {{"kava", type text}, {"kandideerid", Int64.Type}}),

  // Add the "aasta" column
  addAasta = Table.AddColumn(#"Changed column type", "aasta", each Date.Year([date]), Int64.Type),
  
  // -----> Running Total Logic with No Fill Down <-----
  FillMissingValues = Table.Group(addAasta, {"kava", "aasta"}, {
    {"tbl", each let 
        _table = Table.AddIndexColumn(Table.Sort(_, {"date", Order.Ascending}), "index", 0, 1),

        // Initialize a running total list
        RunningTotals = List.Generate(
            () => [CurrentIndex = 0, RunningTotal = null], 
            each [CurrentIndex] < Table.RowCount(_table), 
            each [
                CurrentIndex = [CurrentIndex] + 1, 
                RunningTotal = 
                    if [CurrentIndex] = 0 then 
                        _table[kandideerid]{[CurrentIndex]} 
                    else 
                        if _table[kandideerid]{[CurrentIndex]} = null then 
                            [RunningTotal] 
                        else 
                            if [RunningTotal] = null then 
                                _table[kandideerid]{[CurrentIndex]} 
                            else 
                                [RunningTotal] + _table[kandideerid]{[CurrentIndex]}
            ],
            each [RunningTotal]
        ),
        
        // Add the calculated running total as a new column
        addRTkandideeri = Table.AddColumn(_table, "RTkandideeri", each RunningTotals{[index]})
      in
        addRTkandideeri
    }}
  ),
  
  // Expand the grouped tables
  expandTbl = Table.ExpandTableColumn(FillMissingValues, "tbl", {"date", "RTkandideeri"}, {"date", "RTkandideeri"}),
  
  // Change column types
  changeColType = Table.TransformColumnTypes(expandTbl, {{"date", type date}, {"RTkandideeri", Int64.Type}}),
  
  // Sort the rows by date in descending order
  #"Sorted rows" = Table.Sort(changeColType, {{"date", Order.Descending}})
  
in
  #"Sorted rows";

shared fx_getNextCloestDate = let
  fx_getNextCloestDate = (lookupDate as date, dateTable as table) =>
let
    SortedDates = Table.Sort(dateTable, {{"date", Order.Ascending}}),
    NextDate = Table.SelectRows(SortedDates, each [date] >= lookupDate),
    ClosestDate = if Table.IsEmpty(NextDate) then null else Table.First(NextDate)[date]
in
    ClosestDate
in
  fx_getNextCloestDate;

shared fnCalRunningTotal = let
  fnCalRunningTotal = (CalculationTable as table, KandideeridColumn as text) as list =>
let
    // Sort by date ascending
    SortedTable = Table.Sort(CalculationTable, {"date", Order.Ascending}),
    
    // Add index for ordered calculation
    IndexedTable = Table.AddIndexColumn(SortedTable, "index", 0, 1),

    // Generate Running Totals
    RunningTotals = List.Generate(
        () => [CurrentIndex = 0, RunningTotal = null], 
        each [CurrentIndex] < Table.RowCount(IndexedTable), 
        each [
            CurrentIndex = [CurrentIndex] + 1, 
            RunningTotal = 
                if [CurrentIndex] = 0 then 
                    IndexedTable{[CurrentIndex]}[KandideeridColumn]
                else 
                    if IndexedTable{[CurrentIndex]}[KandideeridColumn] = null then 
                        [RunningTotal] 
                    else 
                        if [RunningTotal] = null then 
                            IndexedTable{[CurrentIndex]}[KandideeridColumn]
                        else 
                            [RunningTotal] + IndexedTable{[CurrentIndex]}[KandideeridColumn]
        ],
        each [RunningTotal]
    )
in
    RunningTotals
in
  fnCalRunningTotal;
